data.description: MAJOR INCENTIVE: Seller will pay up to $10,000 in closing cost with a sold price of $350,000! Use this closing cost incentive as you see fit – for your closing costs, a lower interest rate, or a combination of both! Own a Fontainebleau gem that combines convenience, comfort, and an ideal location. Whether you're a first-time homebuyer searching for the perfect starter home or a student or a faculty member seeking an off-campus residence, this home is for you. Located just a stone's throw away from Tulane University, Loyola University, and St. Mary's Dominican High School, this property offers unmatched convenience for students, faculty, and staff. Say goodbye to long commutes and hello to a stress-free lifestyle. You can reach your campus or school within five minutes, saving valuable time and energy. If you're a first-time homebuyer, this property is an excellent choice for starting your homeownership journey. The cozy layout and manageable size make it easy to maintain and personalize to your taste. Experience worry-free living in your dream home with the added advantage of a BRAND NEW ROOF! Residing in Marlyville/Fontainebleau allows you to relish a wide array of local amenities, immerse yourself in the welcoming community spirit, and embark on exciting adventures exploring the nearby attractions, cafes, shops, and restaurants. If you're looking for an ideal place to call home, Marlyville/Fontainebleau could be your perfect match. Contact us to schedule a tour!
